{"article_id":"YYc9KhyF6XisY3uD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A clip from a 1993 episode of CNN ' s Larry King Live","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"featuring the mother of Biden accuser Tara Reade","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"has seemingly been removed from the Google Play catalog .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The clip is an important piece of information in Reade ' s allegation","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that Biden sexually assaulted her in the same year ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"as it supports her claim","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that she told her mother about the incident .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"In the clip , Reade ' s mother appears to be discussing an incident","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"involving her senator and her daughter ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"without naming either .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"BREAKING :","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Is this the mother of Joe Biden 's accuser","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"talking to CNN in 1993 ?","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"pic.twitter.com/rF7jw35s2F","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"- MediaResearchCenter","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"( @ theMRC )","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"April 24 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Reade ' s mother passed away in 2016 ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"but Reade has confirmed to multiple media organizations","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that she recognizes the voice of the woman","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"speaking to King","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"as her mother .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"CNN claims","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"it can not corroborate","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that the person in the clip is Reade ' s mother .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Fox News confirmed","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that the August 11 , 1993 episode of Larry King Live appears to have vanished from the Google Play catalog .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Twitter user J.L . Hamilton shared a screenshot","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"showing the Aug. 11 , 1993 , broadcast of \" Larry King Live \" was no longer listed in the season three catalog of the iconic CNN talk show .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Mysteriously , though , the Aug. 10 broadcast ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"which is listed as \" Episode 154 \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"is followed by the Aug. 12 broadcast ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"which is listed as \" Episode 155 , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that episode and the ones","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that follow","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"could be incorrectly listed and off by a number .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Fox News later verified","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"the Aug. 11 episode is not listed on the streaming service .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"It is unclear when it was removed from the catalog .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"CNN spokesman Matt Dornic said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"the accusation","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that the clip had been taken down","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"was \" total BS , \"","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that listings on the site are not sourced from the network .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" We do not have a distro deal for [ Larry King Live ] w/ Google play , \"","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"said Dornic .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"\" Listings on the site are not sourced","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"[ through ] CNN .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"True for [ Fox News ] programs too . \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"This is B.S .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"CNN didn ' t remove anything .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"We do not have a distro deal for LKL w/ Google Play .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Listings on the site are not sourced thru CNN .","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"Click any episode ,","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"it will say","depth":16},{"id":57,"text":"\" not available to watch. \"","depth":16},{"id":58,"text":"True for @ foxnews programs too .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"I 